{
  "3285500": {
    "name": "猛将三国",
    "steam_appid": 3285500,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/dfc29d3fa117cdd443fccb7aec851f24.avif?t=1766667910\" width=471 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    公元182年，朝廷积弊难清，民间灾荒不断。为官者因党锢而不敢作为，为民者饱受苦难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    您既可扮演原创角色，也可扮演历史武将，在乱世降临之前努力的建立自己的军事势力和人脉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    您既可以做一个四处游荡的独狼游侠，也可以利用自己的历史知识拉拢诸多名将为你所用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    游戏世界观内容部分来自正史【三国志】部分来自演义【三国演义】以及流行于现代的后世文学作品（会出现王越、童渊等角色）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    如果你喜欢玩三国志游戏系列，或者喜欢太阁立志传系列游戏，那么你不应该错过这个作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/8552cd5024c7ecec5a13d6eeba1bf6bc.avif?t=1766667910\" width=471 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共计登场160+历史角色（以下是部分展示）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/5f472d707ef1cc440683ed096e4c0852.avif?t=1766667910\" width=600 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曹操\t横刀仗剑英雄义，鲜衣怒马正当年。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夏侯惇\t挑灯伏案苦学志，跨马焯枪震天威。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夏侯渊\t游龙跃渊藐四海，我身无拘最疏狂。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >许褚\t但见魔种来降世，虎痴一笑震昆冈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/db7dac87ddd4e9110f6c13141952aa77.avif?t=1766667910\" width=600 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >刘备\t腰悬礼义游龙剑，舌灿贤德金莲花。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关羽\t文骨饱读春秋义，武魂俾睨天下雄。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >张飞\t龙威虎胆寒镔骨，勇烈无双莽撞人。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赵云\t幼龙战天，不堕青云之志。稚蛟闹海，难掩扬波之威。\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/fa2e6b4d0f8e1ebe4a53cba7df06bd0d.avif?t=1766667910\" width=600 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >董卓\t狼腹虎胆谋不臣，鼍口狮心欲吞天。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吕布\t赤目一藐，摧魂、断魄、裂胆，画戟一挥，斩将、夺旗、破军。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >华雄\t金刀烈马风流眼，豺骨狼心也情深。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >张辽\t凇眉雾眼，寒面冷若千秋雪，雄心傲骨，铁血更比烈阳燃。\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/a08109d2ec277f8408908c4ee3e41fe0.avif?t=1766667910\" width=600 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >袁罡\t朱门后，波谲云诡，穷途末路；蓬荜前，蛟龙入海，柳暗花明。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >徐渭\t居篱下，志比鸿鹄亦要偃旗息鼓。且韬光，雄图霸业不做朝夕之争。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >司马胭\t深闺浅泪空遗恨，骨山尸海血断仇。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王姒\t天行有缺道无缺，人心有情剑无情。\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/f68f0b6bda4169427873e3e3fc3ebe16.avif?t=1766667910\" width=600 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >貂蝉\t青葱玉指红酥手，柳眉杏眼绕指柔。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王越\t半生修道半生缘，半步山巅半步仙。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甄姜\t无极甄氏有娇女，含苞待放也倾城。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/a40049bdcc31c690b3617e65c7fc98be.avif?t=1766667910\" width=471 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏包含地图区域：司隶、冀州、幽州、并州、兖州、青州。因为时间线以及工作室的实力所限，没法以完全面貌的十三州展开征战。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/472cb14a181f591b3279e4f756125a75.avif?t=1766667910\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/eec4438ba403dcb958cdd5fdfbd7d281.avif?t=1766667910\" width=471 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >65w+文字文本，自由的养成路线。剿灭流寇，上缴人头，截杀商队，抵抗外族，能想到的任务在游戏中一应俱全。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/635b80eb34eeffcbf6df920b18d2b5ce.avif?t=1766667910\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras_big/635b80eb34eeffcbf6df920b18d2b5ce.avif?t=1766667910 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/67ef19a800e9ec9d60e5152462a0b986.avif?t=1766667910\" width=471 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽量还原古代冷兵器战争体验，初期享受小规模作战的成长乐趣。后期感受大规模兵团作战的史诗感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/d15878460ac4d95e949723ba422eb741.avif?t=1766667910\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras_big/d15878460ac4d95e949723ba422eb741.avif?t=1766667910 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285500/extras/71decc37ea73839f1c780524b1cda2dd.avif?t=1766667910\" width=471 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    游戏初期难度较难，如果没有玩过生存类游戏或者策略类游戏的玩家，请谨慎入手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    对三国武将不太了解的人会比较缺乏代入感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    游戏中没有华丽的战斗画面，喜欢绚丽动作场面的用户慎入。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 日语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 俄语, 韩语, 印度尼西亚语, 菲律宾语",
